<em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yApem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=ba8db20e\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yApem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=2e654e76\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yApem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=1f68617f\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yApem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=75760219\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"2563554ed5ae123a3a1b3776b849be46aa95cf2e","tid":1671412,"uid":250713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"忘記佢啦<br />\n我試過想做返朋友 傾過計出過街 最後都比人放棄了"},{"pid":"7f71cf36505644d3a919fbcbbcbbf8eabbcbcf78","tid":1671412,"uid":144838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:29:38.000Z","msg":"放手啦巴打<br />\n下個更可愛"},{"pid":"6575975a45246b4a25f294fd0d26fef26bae6138","tid":1671412,"uid":12909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2df03295d8ed7a41eaf543d02d14be8408349e6c","tid":1671412,"uid":282536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"仲以為有機會一齊返 今日靠朋友知道左你有鍾意嘅人 知道左個下心都碎哂 原本以為仲有一絲希望 到頭來都係我痴心一片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:59:11.000Z","msg":"只係知道佢有鍾意既人者<br />\n都唔一定無哂機會既<br />\n當初點解會分手既？"},{"pid":"e09fd2a76f6f3e21991e18b83938187e144d4cbf","tid":1671412,"uid":319996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2563554ed5ae123a3a1b3776b849be46aa95cf2e","tid":1671412,"uid":250713,"li